{
  "stem": "7093.7",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "But he put the boy, because he was half-Jewish, into this-- and to make sure-- and he protected this home.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And that's how the other children were also protected.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And therefore-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and these two women really looked after these children wonderfully during the whole war and, and were very, very good to them.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And, and then-- and suddenly, [NON-ENGLISH] put me, a 21-year-old girl-- 21-and-a-half-year-old girl in charge of them, which was as insensitive as it can just be.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "I mean, I was very proud.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "And I was-- I thought it was wonderful.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "And I didn't quite understand first what has happened to me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "But, of course, these two women hated me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "I-- it's quite obvious.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "For, for four years, they were doing their best to look after these children.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "Suddenly, they send them out someone and put someone over them, a 21-year-old girl, which is absolutely terrible.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I didn't-- we didn't have-- also, we had terrible shortages.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had hardly anything to heat with.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had-- we had hardly any potatoes, hardly any food, and no soap.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No medical men.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had-- at one point, I had 12 children ill.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I, I slept with them because I felt that they needed care.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, somebody needed to be with them during the night because some had really high temperature and everything.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was-- when I took on the job, they told me that once a week, I will have a day free.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And once a week, I will have an afternoon free.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, and after six weeks I didn't have one minute free.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was on the verge of collapse.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I phoned and phoned and phoned.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
